OL,3,CUK Government needs to do more on
OL,4,Conline harms, says Scottish minister
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government has urged the
OL,7,FUK Government to do "more to protect
OL,8,Fchildren and young people from online
OL,9,Fharm".
OL,11,FScottish Minister for Children,
OL,12,FSiobhian Brown, is due to meet the UK
OL,13,FMinister for AI and Online Safety
OL,14,FKanishka Narayan on Sunday.
OL,16,FMs Brown said she would "call for
OL,17,Furgent action to protect young people"
OL,18,Fduring the meeting.
