OL,3,CUK Government needs to do more on
OL,4,Conline harms, says Scottish minister
OL,6,FIt comes amid widespread expectation
OL,7,Fthat Sir Keir Starmer will announce a
OL,8,Fban on under-16s being able to access
OL,9,Fharmful social media sites following
OL,10,Fthe Government's consultation on what
OL,11,Frestrictions should be introduced.
OL,13,FThe consultation received around
OL,14,F116,000 responses, making it the
OL,15,Fsecond-largest government consultation
OL,16,Fin history after a consultation on
OL,17,Fequal marriage in 2012.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
