OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781401664
OL,3,CUK Government needs to do more on
OL,4,Conline harms, says Scottish minister
OL,6,FSpeaking before the meeting, Ms Brown,
OL,7,FMinister for Children, Young People
OL,8,Fand The Promise, said: "We need to do
OL,9,Fso much more to protect children and
OL,10,Fyoung people from online harm.
OL,12,F"We've been consistently pushing the
OL,13,FUK Government to act, given the powers
OL,14,Fto control online safety are reserved
OL,15,Fto Westminster.
OL,17,F"One of my first acts as Minister was
OL,18,Fto write to the UK Government to push
OL,19,Ffor urgent action, so I hope there
OL,20,Fwill now finally be some substantive
OL,21,Fsteps taken.
OL,26,@pD@XOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
