PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781401664
OL,3,CUK Government needs to do more on
OL,4,Conline harms, says Scottish minister
OL,6,F"We know there are steps that the UK
OL,7,FGovernment could be taking now ` from
OL,8,Fbanning the use of social media for
OL,9,Fchildren and using Ofcom's powers to
OL,10,Fforce social media firms to act."
OL,12,FAn Institute for Public Policy
OL,13,FResearch (IPPR) survey of more than
OL,14,F2,000 adults, carried out over
OL,15,FWednesday and Thursday, found 51%
OL,16,Ftrust parents to decide which
OL,17,Fplatforms are appropriate, 49% trust
OL,18,Fan independent regulator, 22% trust
OL,19,Fschools, 16% trust technology
OL,20,Fcompanies and 15% trust government
OL,21,Fministers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
