OL,3,CUK Government needs to do more on
OL,4,Conline harms, says Scottish minister
OL,6,FThe polling, conducted by YouGov, also
OL,7,Ffound 44% support banning under-16s
OL,8,Ffrom social media, while 39% prefer
OL,9,Ftighter regulation.
OL,11,FMs Brown added: "Scottish Ministers
OL,12,Fhave been consistently clear that
OL,13,Fsocial media providers must be held to
OL,14,Faccount and have a responsibility to
OL,15,Fproperly enforce their own policies on
OL,16,Fharmful online content.
OL,26,@sD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
