PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781401664
OL,3,CUK Government needs to do more on
OL,4,Conline harms, says Scottish minister
OL,6,F"I want to see, for example, the
OL,7,Fintroduction of a Social Media Levy,
OL,8,Fcharging social media platforms a fee
OL,9,Fwhich can be reinvested back into
OL,10,Fprogrammes for young people's mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,F"In Scotland, our aim is to tackle
OL,14,Fthis issue as a public health matter,
OL,15,Frecognising that there is a spectrum
OL,16,Fof harm that can be caused from the
OL,17,Fabsorption of hateful and harmful
OL,18,Fcontent and unhealthy use of online
OL,19,Fservices."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@JO]
